&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to work as a practice educator within the practice education team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This full time post is to lead the pre-registration programme at WVT, providing expert advice and guidance for all pre-registration students and managers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Specialising in supporting pre-registration nursing students and registered health care professionals, the post holder will liaise with practice placements and HEI&#39;s to facilitate an environment conducive to an excellent learning experience for our future workforce.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To find out more about the post, or for an informal discussion, please contact lynn.carpenter@wvt.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
